OL,3,CSchool-run driver had 'tunnel vision'
OL,4,Cbefore hitting teen, inquest told
OL,6,FA school-run driver whose car hit a
OL,7,Fgirl standing at a bus stop has told
OL,8,Fher inquest how he felt like he was
OL,9,F"falling forwards" as he suffered a
OL,10,Fmedical episode at the wheel.
OL,12,FRichard Brooke, 57, was driving his
OL,13,Fwife's BMW when he lost control and
OL,14,Fhit 15-year-old Katelyn Dawson as she
OL,15,Fwaited for a bus on Wakefield Road,
OL,16,FMoldgreen, Huddersfield in January
OL,17,F2018.
