OL,3,CSchool-run driver had 'tunnel vision'
OL,4,Cbefore hitting teen, inquest told
OL,6,FMr Brooke, who had just dropped his
OL,7,Fson off at school, told the inquest he
OL,8,Fwas not feeling well but felt fit
OL,9,Fenough to drive and had planned to
OL,10,Fwork from home that day.
OL,12,FAs he drove past a church in Wakefield
OL,13,FRoad, Moldgreen, near to the collision
OL,14,Fsite, Mr Brooke said he began to feel
OL,15,F"sick", with "tunnel vision" and a
OL,16,F"feeling of falling forwards".
