OL,3,CSchool-run driver had 'tunnel vision'
OL,4,Cbefore hitting teen, inquest told
OL,6,FMr Brooke said he could not remember
OL,7,Fthe collision and said he felt scared
OL,8,Fand confused. A witness spoke to him
OL,9,Fat the scene and told police the
OL,10,Fdriver had told him he "felt dizzy"
OL,11,Fand was "finding somewhere to pull
OL,12,Fover".
OL,14,FLater, the witness suggested that Mr
OL,15,FBrooke had said: "If I've hurt a child
OL,16,FI'm not going to be able to live my
OL,17,Flife."
