OL,3,CSchool-run driver had 'tunnel vision'
OL,4,Cbefore hitting teen, inquest told
OL,6,FMr Brooke, who appeared via video
OL,7,Flink, appeared to break down when he
OL,8,Fwas shown CCTV footage of the
OL,9,Fcollision and said it was the first
OL,10,Ftime he had seen the video footage.
OL,12,FHe told the court he had been taking
OL,13,Fantibiotics for a cold, a wheezy chest
OL,14,Fand sweats for two days prior to the
OL,15,Fcollision. He said he had not been
OL,16,Ftold to avoid driving.
OL,18,FMr Brooke called what happened a
OL,19,F'tragedy all round' and he could not
OL,20,Fimagine the hurt caused to Katelyn's
OL,21,Fparents, Colin and Angela.
