OL,6,FMr Brooke was in light of the medical
OL,7,Fevidence that he had suffered a
OL,8,Ffainting episode while at the wheel.
OL,10,FLast week, the inquest heard that the
OL,11,Fa set of red traffic lights before it
OL,12,Fcrashed into the bus stop. Katelyn,
OL,13,F15, died later in hospital. Two others
OL,14,Fsuffered serious injuries.
OL,16,FThe Shelley College student suffered
OL,17,Fmultiple injuries and died at Leeds
OL,18,FGeneral Infirmary.
OL,20,FHundreds of her peers for her in the
OL,21,Fdays after her death.
